All symbols pay from left to right on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost reel.

This is the SCATTER symbol.
It appears on all reels.
SCATTERS explode as part of 
the COLOR TUMBLE feature and are 
collected during the sequence.

This is the WILD symbol.
It appears on reels 2, 3 and 4.
It substitutes for all symbols
except for SCATTER symbol.

5x or more SCATTER symbol pays 15x total bet.
4x SCATTER symbol pays 5x total bet.
3x SCATTER symbol pays 2x total bet.

The COLOR TUMBLE feature means that after every paying symbol win all clusters of minimum 5 symbols
with backgrounds of the same color, adjacent anywhere horizontally or vertically, explode and disappear.
The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with symbols
coming from above.
Color tumbling will start only if there is at least one background color cluster present on the screen after any paying
symbol win. Tumbling will continue until there are no more background color cluster present on the screen after any paying
symbol win . Tumbling will continue until there are no more background color clusters present on the screen.
All symbols exploded as part of the COLOR TUMBLE feature get collected in a meter. For every 20 symbols collected
a random multiplier is either added to or multiplies a win multiplier. Possible added values are: +1x, +2x, +3x, +4x,
+5x, +6x, +7x, +8x, +9x, +10x, +15x, +20x, +25x, +30x, +50x and possible multiplying values are: x2, x3, x5, x10. The
win multiplier applies to the total of all wins resulted from the same base spin, after all color tumbles ended. The
multiplier resets back to 1x after every base game spin.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the paying symbol wins and color
tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.

Hit or collect 3 or more SCATTER symbols to trigger the Free spins feature.
The round starts with 15 free spins.
The round has a progressive feature. All symbols collected as part of the COLOR TUMBLE feature count towards the
increse of the win multiplier which does not reset between free spins until the end of the round.
Hit or collect 3, 4 or 5 or more SCATTER symbols during the round, on the same free spin, to retrigger the feature and
get 5, 10 or 15 additional free spins respectively.
Special reels are in play during the feature.

The maximum win amount is limited to 8,000x bet. If the total win of a round reaches 8,000x bet
the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining features are forfeited.

The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently.
The possible values are:
Bet multiplier 25x - the chance to win the FREE SPINS round naturally is higher. More SCATTER symbols
are present on the reels. The BUY FREE SPINS feature is disabled.
Bet multiplier 20x - Normal play.

The FREE SPINS round can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet.
When buying the FREE SPINS round, on the triggering spin 3, 4 or 5 SCATTERS can hit randomly.

All symbols pay from left to right on selected paylines. All wins are multiplied by bet per line.
Free spins and bonus wins are added to the payline win.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Only the highest win is paid per line.
When winning on multiple paylines, all wins are added to the total win.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
